These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, hamster
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Pet   | hamster | chinchilla | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, epic, superhero
1. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | superhero | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, futuristic
1. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
2. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, avocado, lime
1. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Food   | cranberry | lime | avocado |

